| ID          | number       |
| Name        | varchar2(17) |
| CountryCode | varchar2(3)  |
| District    | varchar(10)  |
| Population  | number       |
+-------------+--------------+

Solution:

SELECT * FROM CITY;

4. Query all columns for a city in CITY with the ID 1661.

The CITY table is described as follows:

+-------------+--------------+
