| Name        | varchar2(17) |
| CountryCode | varchar2(3)  |
| District    | varchar(10)  |
| Population  | number       |
+-------------+--------------+

Solution:

SELECT * FROM CITY
WHERE ID = 1661;

5. Japanese Cities' Attributes
